The paper discusses the use of genetic algorithms for efficient adaptation on fitness functions, which is a topic commonly studied in the field of neural networks (cs.NE) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the problem of interacting attributes in data-mining, which falls under the category of data mining (cs.DM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper presents an experiment on the MAX 3-SAT problem, which is a well-known problem in the field of computational complexity (cs.CC).
